dataset<- read.csv("Advertising.csv")
dataset$TV2=dataset$TV**2
pmodel<- lm(Sales~poly(TV,2),data=dataset)
lmodel <- lm(Sales~TV, data=dataset)
summary(lmodel)

abline(lmodel,col="green")
lines(x,y,col="blue")
